<title>Open a file</title>

<p>
<app>Eiciel</app> can be open from the <app>Files</app> application
or standalone. Both scenarios only differ in the way the files are opened.
For the rest they are the same.
</p>

<section id="open-standalone">

<title>Standalone application</title>
<p>
When you start <app>Eiciel</app> no file is opened. You can open a file
pressing <gui style="button">Open file</gui>. If you want to open a directory
use <gui style="button">Open directory</gui>. I both cases a selection dialog will
appear where you can choose a file or a directory.
</p>

<figure>
