</figure>

</section>

<section id="open-nautilus">
<title><app>GNOME Files</app></title>
<p>
In <app>GNOME Files</app> right-click on the file or directory. Then press <gui style="menuitem">Edit Access Control Listâ€¦</gui>. This will start Eiciel directly in ACL editing mode.
</p>

<figure>
	<title>Opening a file in <app>GNOME Files</app></title>
    <media type="image" src="figures/open_file_nautilus.png"/>
